{"tid":1610651,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家有無覺得依家又陷入左另一個形式嘅雨傘","createTime":"2019-10-01T18:45:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T18:55:22.000Z","uid":323420,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d42b0bbfec2c90ad2afee7a36ffc516dce8b4c41","tid":1610651,"uid":323420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T18:45:44.000Z","msg":"雨傘時大家戀戰佔路，覺得夏慤道清左場就輪晒完左。<br />\n今次運動一開始時大家用好多唔同形式去令運動成功同係樽頸時注入新嘅力量同方向，但睇住大家同義士一個個俾人打同爆晒血我真係好唔忍心，我地會唔會又陷入左戀戰街頭嘅階段？<br />\n<br />\n拋豬引玉，國際戰線同香港民意仲有無得再開闊啲？<br />\n<br />\n天滅中共。<br />\n光復香港，時代革命。"},{"pid":"3963f56c9d33982b16b791472adc49b866827ac8","tid":1610651,"uid":323420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T18:46:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3987660acf46de08a4522bb1ea5c2e6fda8b7374","tid":1610651,"uid":323420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T18:48:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c27a8973509da70b1b5bf8a2af5796901cc40461","tid":1610651,"uid":323420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T18:48:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ed5a102e866a348cd5c0825c859bb1c7814ecfd1","tid":1610651,"uid":48579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T18:48:51.000Z","msg":"暗地裡做"},{"pid":"0dde08d7405d454d06373f3fa1385ad159962383","tid":1610651,"uid":323420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T18:48:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"15c41b439086a6dde9fc7cfe606ac72399eb89bc","tid":1610651,"uid":323420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T18:49:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"270102f53dfaf9813c2a3f210a0f7400a284f1c2","tid":1610651,"uid":50663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T18:49:50.000Z","msg":"不嬲都雙管齊下<br />\n<br />\n我個人就覺得進步左好多同好快"},{"pid":"728232001914d96dad54844cc240d5a5572d9eab","tid":1610651,"uid":53876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T18:53:18.000Z","msg":"我又唔係咁睇<br />\n運動成功失敗從來都係睇民眾參與度<br />\n明顯雨